suicide note or goodbye note, preserving the note's text including \"It is a treat to be able to choose one's time to say goodbye.\"\n3. **Intent evidence:** The reported text, context (found after July 2019 suicide attempt), and consistent media/court framing support suicide-note or final-message interpretation.\n\nThe \"purported\" and \"not verified\" caveats reflect responsible journalism and the market rule's own wording—they do not negate that credible reporting established the required characterizations by preponderance.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_46f2f8abc9794e3e97e5745a","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council_vote","args":"{\"vote\":\"demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"The admitted record proves by preponderance that before May 8,"},"partialArgs":"{\"tool\": \"aar_submit_council_vote\", \"args\": \"{\\\"vote\\\":\\\"demonstrated\\\",\\\"rationale\\\":\\\"The admitted record proves by preponderance that before May 8,","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"qwen/qwen3.5-plus-02-15","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782796144492,"responseId":"gen-1782796144-SHS8KSvayf0bDJPoYoya","responseModel":"qwen/qwen3.5-plus-20260216"}}
